This is exactly correct...your mistake is to lump mages into the &quot;real damage dealers&quot; category.  We havent been there since shortly after the release of rok.  Meeles of similar level with slightly above average gear do anywhere from slightly less (warriors) to way more (rogue dps is sick &amp; wrong) damage than magicians in most cases now &amp; have the added ability to do things like take hits and to function normally during overpulls (where as a mage all you can do is spam /pet backoff while the chanter gets things under control) &amp; not die in more than 5 hits.<br>
